# Temperature Simulator

## Overview

This project simulates temperature monitoring using Arduino and a temperature sensor in Tinkercad.

## Components Used

* Arduino Uno
* Temperature Sensor
* Breadboard
* Jumper Wires

## Working

The temperature sensor continuously measures temperature values. The Arduino reads the sensor data and processes the temperature readings.

## Applications

* Weather Monitoring
* Smart Home Systems
* Environmental Monitoring

## Skills Learned

* Sensor Interfacing
* Analog Input Reading
* Arduino Programming
* Data Monitoring
